iCenter API 认证流程：
1. 认证接口: POST http://uac.zte.com.cn/uaccommauth/auth/comm/verify.serv
2. 签名算法: MD5(username + password + timestamp)
3. 请求参数: {username, timestamp, signature}
4. 响应格式: {code: 0, data: {token: "xxx"}, message: ""}
5. 文档创建接口: POST https://icenterapi.zte.com.cn/zte-rd-icenter-contents/content/
6. 请求头: Authorization: Bearer {token}
7. 请求体: {title, content, type: "article"}
